---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_EMAIL, SITE_LOCATION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<section class="about-hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
		<h1>From outside Austin to Harvard football to Axon, the through-line has always been competition, discipline, and growth.</h1>
		<p>
			I like building in environments that reward discipline, fast learning, and the ability to
			execute under pressure. Sports shaped that early, and the same mindset still carries over into
			how I approach work now.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="about-grid">
		<div class="card">
			<h2>Short bio</h2>
			<p>
				I was born and raised outside Austin, Texas, and grew up playing sports year-round. That led
				me to Harvard, where I played football and studied economics. Being part of a high-level team
				environment taught me how much I enjoy challenge, structure, and pushing toward difficult
				goals with other ambitious people.
			</p>
			<p>
				Today I am based in Scottsdale and work at Axon in its Leadership Development Program. I have
				spent time around AI software development and broader tech work, and I am interested in the
				kinds of problems that sit at the intersection of product, execution, and real-world impact.
			</p>
			<p>
				Outside of work, I stay active, lift, play sports, and unwind with video games. I like
				competition, I like improvement, and I like building a life that has some balance between
				serious work and things that are just fun.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h2>What I am focused on</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Growing as an operator and leader inside technology organizations</li>
				<li>Learning faster by building projects instead of just talking about them</li>
				<li>Exploring AI and software opportunities with real-world usefulness</li>
				<li>Staying competitive, active, and disciplined outside of work too</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="contact card">
		<h2>Contact</h2>
		<p>{SITE_LOCATION}</p>
		<p>
			<a href={`mailto:${SITE_EMAIL}`}>{SITE_EMAIL}</a>
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about-hero {
		max-width: 48rem;
		padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
	}
	.eyebrow {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: rgb(var(--muted));
	}
	.about-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 5rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.card {
		padding: 1.35rem;
		border-radius: 24px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--border), 0.9);
		background: rgba(var(--paper-rgb), 0.72);
	}
	.contact {
		max-width: 28rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.about-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
